'''Small Lizards''' are [[Slayer monsters]] found north-north- east of [[Nardah]] east of fairy ring (DLQ). An [[Ice cooler]] must be used on a lizard when it has 1-4 hitpoints left in order to kill it. They can be killed for [[Desert Lizard]] [[slayer task]]s.

